The paper discusses testing practices for machine learning programs, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the paper mentions deep learning and reinforcement learning, which are subfields of machine learning and are often categorized under cs.LG (machine learning). The paper also discusses the importance of reliability in safety-critical systems, which could fall under the systems and control (cs.SY) category. Finally, the paper mentions the need to detect and correct faults in ML programs, which could fall under the cryptography and security (cs.CR) category.
